  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook the lasagna noodles according to the package instructions.",
    "In a medium bowl, combine the yuzu-cure, minced garlic, salt, and pepper. ",
    "In a large bowl, combine the taleggio cheese, chopped parsley, lemon juice, and olive oil.",
    "In a separate bowl, combine the cooked lasagna noodles, the yuzu-cure mixture, and the taleggio cheese mixture. ",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish and spread it evenly. ",
    "Sprinkle the nutritional yeast and oregano over the top of the lasagna. ",
    "Cover the dish with aluminum foil and bake for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove the foil and continue baking for an additional 10-15 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Let the lasagna rest for 10-15 minutes before serving."
